race.comment: BLUE BLEND (2) has a strong overall record having 14 wins and eight places from 31 starts including a last start success (24.96) over 457m at this track. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Looks the testing material here. STAR TURN (1) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 2.75 lengths at this track in a handy 25.17. Can make it two on the bounce. FIRE ME UP (7) goes very well at the course and distance with five wins and a placing from seven starts. Scored by 4.5 lengths last time (25.08) in a OPEN over 457m at this track. Looks one of the chances. SUPER SCRUB (8) comes off a (25.08) win last time, scoring by 4 lengths in a OPEN over 457m at this track. Has already won seven times from this draw.
